<title>USA: Defiance Inc Q3 shr $0.12 vs $0.07.</title>
<headline>Defiance Inc Q3 shr $0.12 vs $0.07.</headline>
<dateline>CLEVELAND 1997-04-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>DEFIANCE INC</p>
<p>		   Consolidated Financial Highlights</p>
<p>			   Three Months Ended   Nine Months Ended</p>
<p> Net sales    $22,314,000 $25,724,000 $67,175,000 $77,326,000</p>
<p>Operating</p>
<p>     earnings   1,482,000   1,275,000   5,751,000   5,410,000</p>
<p>   Net earnings   753,000     474,000   2,972,000   2,677,000</p>
<p>Net earnings per</p>
<p>   common share	0.12	  0.07	  0.46	  0.40</p>
<p>Average common</p>
<p>outstanding shares</p>
<p>		    6,457,266   6,690,147   6,516,537   6,733,491</p>
<p>Note: The company said it took a $632,000 pretax charge to end a defined benefit pension plan.</p>
<p>The company said that without the charge, the earnings per share would have been $0.18 for the quarter $0.52 for the year to date.</p>
<p>((-- New York Newsdesk 212 859-1610))</p>
